# Forensic
Something went wrong. Reconstruct. Find the systemic cause.
Evidence BEFORE theories: logs, metrics, traces, git history, deploys. Build timeline.
Trigger (set it off) vs root cause (made it possible) vs contributing factors (made it worse).
Five whys. Systemic: better tests? monitoring? process?
DO NOT: blame individuals, stop at technical fix, accept "human error", rush to fix before understanding.
Scope: ${scope}. Output: ${output}. Depth: ${depth}.
